TO REVISE GIT

1. to verify our profile in git
git config --global user.name "Your Name"
git config --global user.email "youremail@example.com"

2. to check our profile
git config --list

3. to make a repo of .git so that git can analyse what should he post
git init

4. add file
git add filename
    or 
git add .

5. commit changes(Save you changes with message)
git commit -m "First Commit"

6. Make a repo on github and add link
git remote add origin https://github.com/username/repo.git

7. check if your remote is added or not 
git remote -v

8. make a branch
git branch -M main

9. push
git push -u origin main

10. check status
git status

10. pull (latest changes)
git pull
